latestIgtvVideos.title: Someone to Lava 🎶
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
From the Disney short “Someone to Lava.” I’m learning that it’s really hard to sing and play a musical instrument at the same time but the kind of focus it brings is incredible! I’m still new at this and it’s a little rough especially towards the end but this is a cute song and I had fun ♥️ @cynthialinmusic has some super easy and interesting tutorials up on YouTube that I’ve been following. Thank you Cynthia ✨

latestPosts.caption:
Surfing with the right people feels like more than just a sport. It feels like belonging. 

There’s something surreal about Indian surf sisters coming together from around the world, sharing waves, laughter and a whole lot of stoke in the motherland 🤙🏾

To more shaka, more surf, and more brown women in the water!🏄🏽‍♀️🌊🩵

📸 Clicked by @dustinellisonphoto - OG surf brother. 

#Surfing #India #LongBoarding #SurfSisterhood #WomenWhoSurf #SurfCulture #LadySliders #RepresentationMatters
